select count(*) FROM [dbo].[FaresData_Slow2] 
 select count(*) FROM [dbo].[FaresData_Fast2] 

select 
    min (mta_tax) mta_tax,
    max(total_amount) total_amount ,
    avg(id) id_avg,
    count(distinct surcharge) surcharge
from dbo.FaresData_Fast2
group by [payment_type]

select 
    min (mta_tax) mta_tax,
    max(total_amount) total_amount ,
    avg(id) id_avg,
    count(distinct surcharge) surcharge
from dbo.FaresData_Slow2
group by [payment_type]
